	@@.mc-thoughts; It pushes in. Slow, then less slow. Whatever's down there isn't in a hurry to leave you, and your body, your stupid honest body, is already deciding how it feels about that. Then the thing inside you finishes, hot and a@@
	<<linkappend "@@.usebtn; lot of it@@">>
		<<video "mechanics/tentacles/witch-t2.mp4">>
		@@.mc-thoughts; Then the grip eases. The wet weight slides out of you and away into the dark, leaving you wet down both thighs and not quite the same person who walked in. You let yourself out. Quietly. The key is wherever it was before; you don't look.@@<br><br>
